{"lastUpdated":"2026-06-16T23:53:34.324Z","seriesId":95483,"title":"ToHeart Remember my memories","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31872603/31872603.42021351","descriptionFirst":"高校三年生の春をむかえた浩之とあかり。校内では、サッカーの有望選手として注目される雅史の新聞記事が話題になっていた。浩之は、ふとその新聞に載っている広告欄を見て…。\n\n藤田浩之:一条和矢／神岸あかり:川澄綾子／マルチ:堀江由衣／長岡志保:樋口智恵子／来栖川綾香:岩男潤子／保科智子:久川綾／松原葵:飯塚雅弓／姫川琴音:氷上恭子／宮内レミィ:笠原留美／セリオ:根谷美智子／佐藤雅史:保志総一朗\n\n原作:AQUAPLUS／監督:元永慶太郎／脚本:叶希一／キャラクターデザイン・総作画監督:平山まどか／美術監督:前田実／音響監督:明田川仁／アニメーション制作:OLM/AICA.S.T.A.／製作:THRWorks\n\n次話→so31872749","tags":["エロゲ・エロアニメ原作","O.L.M","2004年秋アニメ","LEAF・アクアプラス","1期は未配信","恋愛/ラブコメ"],"cours":"2004-秋","colKey":"た","relatedSeries":[],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so31872603","episodeNo":1,"title":"ToHeart Remember my memories　1話　｢新しい予感｣","viewCounter":2643,"commentCounter":42,"mylistCounter":72,"lengthSeconds":1443,"startTime":"2012-06-27T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31872603/31872603.42021351"},{"contentId":"so31872749","episodeNo":2,"title":"ToHeart Remember my memories　2話　｢昔と､今と｣","viewCounter":628,"commentCounter":12,"mylistCounter":4,"lengthSeconds":1443,"startTime":"2012-06-27T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31872749/31872749.57692802"},{"contentId":"so31872750","episodeNo":3,"title":"ToHeart Remember my memories　3話　｢そして､君は｣","viewCounter":465,"commentCounter":31,"mylistCounter":2,"lengthSeconds":1442,"startTime":"2012-06-27T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31872750/31872750.12167293"},{"contentId":"so31874044","episodeNo":4,"title":"ToHeart Remember my memories　4話　｢強さと､優しさ｣","viewCounter":429,"commentCounter":20,"mylistCounter":2,"lengthSeconds":1443,"startTime":"2012-06-27T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31874044/31874044.74825120"},{"contentId":"so31874045","episodeNo":5,"title":"ToHeart Remember my memories　5話　｢越えるべき壁｣","viewCounter":436,"commentCounter":24,"mylistCounter":3,"lengthSe